    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è Today, I am going to show you. How to use hex color in bootstrap with code example. Hexadecimal Colors Hexadecimal color‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you. <strong><em>How to use hex color in bootstrap</em></strong> with code example.</p>\n<h3>Hexadecimal Colors</h3>\n<p>Hexadecimal color values are also supported in all browsers.</p>\n<p>A hexadecimal color is specified with: <code class=\"language-text\">#RRGGBB</code>.</p>\n<p>RR <code class=\"language-text\">(red)</code>, GG <code class=\"language-text\">(green)</code> and BB <code class=\"language-text\">(blue)</code> are hexadecimal integers between <code class=\"language-text\">00</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">FF</code> specifying the intensity of the color.</p>\n<p>For example, <code class=\"language-text\">#0000FF</code> is displayed as blue, because the blue component is set to its highest value <code class=\"language-text\">(FF)</code> and the others are set to 00.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Includes bootstrap view</li>\n<li>Includes bootstrap libraries</li>\n<li>Includes bootstrap js libraries</li>\n<li>Define its class name</li>\n<li>Includes css in html page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This article will guide you to adding hex color in Bootstrap with example.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Includes bootstrap view</h3>\n<p>To ensure proper rendering and touch zooming for all devices, add the responsive viewport meta tag to your <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head></code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>viewport<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>width=device-width, initial-scale=1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Includes bootstrap libraries</h3>\n<p>First of all, load the Bootstrap framework CSS into the head tag of your webpage.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"> <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Bootstrap CSS --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/c@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">integrity</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">crossorigin</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>anonymous<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Includes bootstrap js libraries</h3>\n<p>Now, load the Bootstrap JavaScript file before closing the body tag and done.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">integrity</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">crossorigin</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>anonymous<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 4: Define its class name</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>But I must explain to you how all this .<span class=\"token tag\"><spa